node.text: How to work smarter in six steps 💡

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Business & Entrepreneur on August 04, 2021 tagging @entrepreneursquote. May be an image of text that says 'How to work smarter By @entrepreneursquote (Swipe left)'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Focus on one task at a time Studies have shown that when you switch from one task to another, you actually waste time because of the time it takes your brain to switch tasks and change its focus.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Keep your to-do do list short Keep your to-do list short and focus on three to five important and challenging tasks for the day your most important tasks that, once completed, will make you feel highly productive.'.

Photo by Business & Entrepreneur on August 04, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Respond quickly Get in the habit of responding to people right away If you open an email that requires a response, take the time to respond right away SO the task is off your list immediately.'.
